org.xbib.elasticsearch.plugin.jdbc

Class PlainIndexableObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.xbib.elasticsearch.plugin.jdbc.PlainIndexableObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<IndexableObject>, org.elasticsearch.common.xcontent.ToXContent, IndexableObject

    public class PlainIndexableObject
extends Object
implements IndexableObject, org.elasticsearch.common.xcontent.ToXContent, Comparable<IndexableObject>
    A plain indexable object. The indexable object can store meta data and core data. The indexable object can be iterated and passed to an XContentBuilder. The individual values are formatted for JSON, which should be the correct format
